{"tid":2251171,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"陳奕迅稱很久沒有收入了！(『荷包乾硬化』同『急性發錢寒』)","createTime":"2020-10-20T15:07:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-20T18:39:14.000Z","uid":318316,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"61961501bb5b5f0dedb92b7c5387287fba102779","tid":2251171,"uid":318316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T15:07:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/RXyd25OR8XTsPjzVPJtlvQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgwO2g9NTU3/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-10/137d2240-129f-11eb-bdeb-a56ce4b81178\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FRXyd25OR8XTsPjzVPJtlvQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzgwO2g9NTU3%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-10%2F137d2240-129f-11eb-bdeb-a56ce4b81178&h=9134a09c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n談到疫情對他的影響，問到近一年都停工？他即自爆患病：「我患咗『荷包乾硬化』同『急性發錢寒』，哈哈，其實好多人都係咁，只係我藉機會公開呢個病。（蝕咗幾多錢？）唔知，之前收入好平均，但好耐冇見到有加號，但我有積穀防饑。（幾時恢復工作？）呢年以嚟淨係拍過快餐店廣告同錄音。」<br />\n<br />\n未知幾時開番個唱<br />\n<br />\n問到去年取消的跨年演唱會何時會舉行？他笑言知道有傳楊千嬅爭贏他奪得今年年尾紅館檔期：「但我冇爭過，我冇入紙申請。（幾時開番演唱會？）講真未知係咪真係開到，我知道2021年應該冇乜期，因為聽聞今年取消嗰啲可以優先揀番出年，但我係上年，而且我要book好長嘅期，如果唔係補唔番製作費，哈哈，上年開25場，我要35-40日先得，因為預中間要抖。（心急開騷？）已經唔急啦。」 <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.celebrity.yahoo.com/%E7%96%AB%E5%A2%83%E5%B9%BE%E4%B9%8E%E9%9B%B6%E6%94%B6%E5%85%A5%E9%99%B3%E5%A5%95%E8%BF%85%E8%87%AA%E7%88%86%E6%82%A3%E7%97%85%E6%88%B6%E5%8F%A3%E5%A5%BD%E8%80%90%E5%86%87%E8%A6%8B%E9%81%8E%E5%8A%A0%E8%99%9F-064114711.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.celebrity.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%2596%25AB%25E5%25A2%2583%25E5%25B9%25BE%25E4%25B9%258E%25E9%259B%25B6%25E6%2594%25B6%25E5%2585%25A5%25E9%2599%25B3%25E5%25A5%2595%25E8%25BF%2585%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2588%2586%25E6%2582%25A3%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%2588%25B6%25E5%258F%25A3%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E8%2580%2590%25E5%2586%2587%25E8%25A6%258B%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%258A%25A0%2